@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. 客户注册 - 成功 (201 Created)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "phone": "13800001111",
  "address": "北京市海淀区"
}

### 2. 客户注册 - 用户名重复 (409 Conflict)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 客户注册 - 用户名过短 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ab",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. 客户注册 - 用户名为空 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. 客户注册 - 密码过短 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "12345"
}

### 6. 客户注册 - 邮箱格式错误 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "invalid-email"
}

### 7. 查询客户 - 成功 (200 OK)
# 请将 1 替换为注册成功后返回的 id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1

### 8. 查询客户 - 不存在 (404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/99999

### 9. 修改客户信息 - 成功 (200 OK)
# 请将 1 替换为注册成功后返回的 id
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "phone": "13900002222",
  "address": "上海市浦东新区"
}

### 10. 修改客户信息 - 不存在 (404 Not Found)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/99999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}
